---
layout: base.njk
title: Feed
description: Life updates and writing by Kevin Barcenas-Martinez.
permalink: /feed/
---

<h1>Feed</h1>

{% if collections.posts.length == 0 %}
  <p class="empty">Nothing here yet, I'm working on a nice workflow where posts will be pushed from Obsidian via Enveloppe to appear here.</p>
{% else %}
  <ol class="post-list" reversed>
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <span class="date">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</span>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
{% endif %}
